Output demos/verification-loop.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 750
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Framerate 30
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Padding 20

Hide
Type "python3 demos/demo-shell.py verification-loop"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

# Run prompt with verification loop
Type "/run-prompt 010 --loop --max-iterations 5"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 5000ms
